{"tid":970652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳洲科學教命案】16歲台少年阻母「淨化」殺人 教會驚人學費曝光","createTime":"2019-01-06T04:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:56:02.000Z","uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6052f4f6f02f384a8a62744ee16a76286dc6369","tid":970652,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546691773_152b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546691773_152b.jpg&h=334eb63f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲科學教教會發生的命案有更多案情曝光。(互聯網)<br />\n一名16歲台灣少年日前在澳洲悉尼車士活區（Chatswood）的科學教（Scientology）澳洲總部，用刀襲擊2名男職員，其中一名24歲台灣男子被割頸身亡，案件有更多內情曝光！原來少年當時正在阻止母親接受「淨化儀式」，雙方發生爭執，少年被強行趕走，最終發生憾事。這名少年昨日（5日）正式被落案控以謀殺罪。案件同時揭發，有「虛擬伊甸園」之稱的科學教澳洲總部的驚人課程價錢，每小時高達800澳元（約4,463港元），但信徒仍對此趨之若鶩。<br />\n事發前一晚，這名16歲台灣少年曾哀求母親不要參加教會的「淨化儀式」；至儀式當日，母親仍一意孤行，少年為了阻止母親，更一度發生衝突。少年本月3日被數名科學教職員要求離開教會時發難，從車上拿出一把25厘米的長刀，刺死了送他離開的24歲台灣男子Aaron，另刺傷了30歲男子的手部，並且襲擊了一名叫Penny Teng的女子及另一名叫Joel Lawrence的男子。<br />\n根據澳洲法例，由於這名少年尚未年滿18歲，他的名字沒有被公開。少年除了被控謀殺外，還被控普通襲擊（家庭暴力）（common assault, domestic violence）、襲擊致身體傷害（assault occasioning actual bodily harm and affray）等罪名。案件昨日在帕拉瑪塔市兒童法庭開展保釋聆訊，少年沒有申請保釋。其代表律師轉達少年不想出庭的意願，並要求案件於下周一（7日）繼續聆訊時，提供一名中文繙譯。<br />\n此外，案件亦將公眾目光投放到車士活區的科學教教會上。這間教會是科學教的亞太區總部，佔地1.35萬平方米，於2016年9月開幕，是美國以外最大的科學教教會；只有地位較高的信眾，可在科學教教會內活動，課程費用更高達每小時800澳元。教會位於蘭灣國家公園（Lane Cove National Park）及藍桉步道（Blue Gum Creek）附近，被形容為「虛擬的伊甸園」。<br />\n澳洲科學教教會內，有60個靈修室，讓信眾接受精神教育，並培養新的信眾；教會內設施豐富，猶如一個會所俱樂部，有會議室、健身室、咖啡廳、桑拿房，甚至錄影棚。澳洲科學教教會更提供不少輔導課程，包括繙譯成17種語言的傳教材料，其中包括中文及日文。<br />\n科學教由美國作家哈伯德（L.Ron Hubbard）於1952年創辦，總部位於美國洛杉磯。教派認為每個人都有人生創傷，需找到創傷根源，並透過「淨化」，排除身體內藥物和毒素對心靈的影響來提升生命品質。信眾不乏名人，包括美國著名影星湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/今日悉尼/ABC news<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190106/59107025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59107025&d=ao9E%2F6OdHCl1a577d6iu3TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8dffa128\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59107025&h=a7b9737f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190106/59107025</a>"},{"pid":"e88a3682753d6540f2e2e68a38e663b2cbc9d218","tid":970652,"uid":34241,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"孝子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0ef10cccdff6dd0ed8aa4d2b75dfdc4ca79630","tid":970652,"uid":212399,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YYK8cX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YYK8cX.gif&h=7b41da15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4aa6d8f4215dfbc1e44d09149cfef51d15f67a2","tid":970652,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb66a9b08e3a96eeaa1e3c53b03d880c11c76b9","tid":970652,"uid":182499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"係咪即係山達基？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cff0bf33b436846676f0f870c1ded59d39abc5d","tid":970652,"uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbb66a9b08e3a96eeaa1e3c53b03d880c11c76b9","tid":970652,"uid":182499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"係咪即係山達基？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n山達基（英语：Scientology），非正式中文譯名包括「科學神教」和「科學教」，是一套信仰與修行活動的體系及宗教，由L&middot;羅恩&middot;賀伯特所創立。 山達基教會始於1952年，山達基的前身是賀伯特更早期的一套自我幫助的系統──戴尼提。"},{"pid":"2f302350b26215bf72da8a6c81512df4451d46f0","tid":970652,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"呢個教有無咩害人新聞"},{"pid":"398b3247cdc3677c4bbc03d52b0145ea055977b5","tid":970652,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f302350b26215bf72da8a6c81512df4451d46f0","tid":970652,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"呢個教有無咩害人新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢係依家所有自我提升課程嘅始祖"},{"pid":"6b0fdd9ec638437e44581ecadd15e56c6a606ebc","tid":970652,"uid":171786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"398b3247cdc3677c4bbc03d52b0145ea055977b5","tid":970652,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f302350b26215bf72da8a6c81512df4451d46f0","tid":970652,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"呢個教有無咩害人新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢係依家所有自我提升課程嘅始祖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"哦，即老千界師祖"},{"pid":"16fd97f91edece993ab643b4eb90cba0305792c0","tid":970652,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"殊樂咇咇"},{"pid":"159e4b84dffcc28d4c404ecdd17f8143a9a13fa9","tid":970652,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"clifform"},{"pid":"72f259b6a16dd904177dd5ef53267d39c2e9595f","tid":970652,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b0fdd9ec638437e44581ecadd15e56c6a606ebc","tid":970652,"uid":171786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"398b3247cdc3677c4bbc03d52b0145ea055977b5","tid":970652,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f302350b26215bf72da8a6c81512df4451d46f0","tid":970652,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:10:48.